criteria.driver_alignment:
Validate stage — student states they double-checked results with other AIs (external validation) and describes re-running validation loops;  
Evolve stage — performed sensitivity testing (revenue -20%, WACC ±2%);  
Implement stage — iterated model runs to fix input errors.

Discover: stated scope and intent to evaluate and recommend ("...will be using the driver method... and then give a recommendation.");  
Implement: ran sensitivity tests (revenue -20%, WACC ±2%) to compare outcomes;  
Reflect: interpreted sensitivity results and made a recommendation ("these results do point..." and noted revenue risk).
